Connotation of the new political media.
武汉市青山区市民 夏女士澎湃新闻记者 薛莎莎 整理夏女士家住武汉市青山区，家中七口人：公婆、父母、丈夫、她和三岁大的孩子。
Ms. Xue Sha Sha, a journalist from Qingshan District, Wuhan City, lives in the Qingshan area of Wuhan City. There are seven members of her family: her mother-in-law, her parents, her husband, her three-year-old child.
此前，澎湃新闻（www.thepaper.cn）曾报道了她一家七口疑似感染新冠肺炎的故事。
Earlier, news surged (www.thepper.cn) reporting the story of seven members of her family suspected of contracting pneumonia.
她公婆、丈夫先后查出肺部感染或病变，住进了武汉市第九医院的隔离病房。
Her mother-in-law, her husband has detected lung infection or pathological changes, live in Wuhan City Ninth Hospital isolation ward.
她父母肺部也感染，此前在武汉市中心医院治疗。
Her parents, whose lungs were also infected, had been treated at Wuhan Central Hospital.
随后，公婆、丈夫和母亲所做的新冠病毒核酸检测，均呈阳性。
Subsequently, the mother-in-law, husband and mother-in-law tested positive for the new crown virus nucleic acid.
2月4日上午，夏女士的父亲“突发重症”抢救无效离世，她和家人未能见到父亲最后一面。
On the morning of February 4, Ms. Xia's father died of a "severe attack." She and her family were unable to see her father for the last time.
2月14日，夏女士称，她公公身体基础不好，但仍然战胜了病毒，当日已经出院回家。
On 14 February, Ms. Xia stated that her father-in-law had overcome the virus despite his poor health and had been discharged from the hospital the same day.
她三岁孩子的核酸检测也转阴了，若再测一次还是阴性，也可以出院。
Her three-year-old's nucleic acid test also turned cloudy, if the test is negative again, can also be discharged.
Play夏女士公公出院。
Ms. Play Xia was discharged from hospital.
夏女士提供(00:11)夏女士在输液治疗。
Ms. Xia provides (00: 11) Ms. Xia is undergoing transfusion therapy.
夏女士供图夏女士表示，她想快点好起来，以此激励其他病人。
Ms. Xia said she wanted to get better soon so she could inspire other patients.
如果康复出院，她和老公都想为其他病人捐血浆。
If she recovers from hospital, she and her husband both want to donate plasma to other patients.
澎湃新闻将持续以日记的形式，记录夏女士一家在治疗期间所经历的种种。
The surging news will continue to take the form of a diary of what Ms. Xia's family went through during the treatment.
以下是夏女士的日记：2月14日 星期五 晴今天是我入院的第十一天，身体各项指征都还算平稳。
The following is Ms. Xia's diary: Feb. 14, Fri Fine Today is my eleventh day on the hospital.
早上医生查房说，过两天我再去复查一次，到时候看身体恢复得如何。
The doctor said in the morning that I would go back in a couple of days to see how well I was.
护士每天都会来查氧饱和度、心率、体温，一天来查三四次。
The nurse comes to check oxygen saturation, heart rate, and body temperature three or four times a day.
我的其他指数都正常，就是心率有点快，后背偶尔有点疼，早起的时喉咙有点不舒服。
My other indices are normal, that is, the heart rate is a bit fast, back occasionally a bit painful, early in the throat a bit uncomfortable.
今天的早餐，朋友送来了她亲手做的饼，还送了车厘子。
For breakfast today, a friend brought her homemade cake and a cupcake.
我吃了一顿丰盛的早餐，感觉元气满满。
I had a hearty breakfast and felt full of energy.
治疗以来，我认为好好吃饭真的挺重要。
Since the treatment, I think eating well is really important.
饿的时候，我的精神很差，吃饱后立马感觉有力气了。
When I was hungry, my spirit was poor, and I felt strong immediately after I was full.
听医生说这病是消耗性疾病，所以营养比较重要。
Hear the doctor say this disease is expendables disease, so nutrition is more important.
今天，儿童医院那边说我家宝宝核酸阴性了，如果再检测一次也是阴性，宝宝就可以出院了，我又看到了曙光啦！加油，我也要快点好起来接宝宝回家。
Today, the children's hospital side said my baby Nucleic Acid negative, if a second test is negative, the baby can be discharged, I saw the light! Come on, I have to get up quickly to pick up the baby home.
我希望我快点好起来，给其他病人增加斗志。
I hope I get better soon and increase my morale among the other patients.
等我好了，我想捐血浆，我老公也想捐。
Wait for me. I want to donate plasma. My husband wants to donate, too.
今天最大的好消息是，我公公核酸检测双阴，已经出院回家啦！2020年2月14日本期编辑 常琛推荐阅读。
The best news today is that my father-in-law has been discharged from the hospital with a double yin test.
